General Information
===================

BDSIM version 0.5_dev, Geant4 toolkit for radiation transport in accelerators

The official web site is:
	http://www.pp.rhul.ac.uk/twiki/bin/view/JAI/simulation

The official Geant4 web site is:
	http://geant4.web.cern.ch/geant4/


Maintained by Steve Malton (malton@pp.rhul.ac.uk),
Ilya Agapov (agapov@pp.rhul.ac.uk) and G.A.Blair (blair@pp.rhul.ac.uk)

This release x.x.2008



History
===================

